Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.00,0:01:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(131,281)\fs20\fad(600,900)}在變換的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.12,0:01:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼長時間沒結果的比賽還真少見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全成了消耗戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.20,0:01:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一面承受著強烈的橫向G力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.80,0:01:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一面持續著極度的緊張狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.93,0:01:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對肉體與精神的負擔都非同小可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.42,0:02:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況在這樣棘手的賽道上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.03,0:02:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般人早就嘔吐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.72,0:02:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耐力成了勝負的關鍵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.78,0:02:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能確定的 就是先失去注意力的人會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.92,0:02:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和美就這麼回埼玉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.86,0:02:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許再也見不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.26,0:02:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦才好? 怎麼辦才好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這句話 如果連這句話都不說出來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然也不能改變什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.32,0:02:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可我要說「喜歡和美」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.82,0:02:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.17,0:02:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.33,0:02:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三輪來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人都幹勁十足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.58,0:03:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看得我手都癢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.19,0:03:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,LEVIN也和第一輪先行時不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.37,0:03:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有兩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.49,0:03:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和剛才的跑法完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快得出奇 完全不留餘地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一輪我並沒想留手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.93,0:03:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不清楚道路狀況的最初一輪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.68,0:03:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用百分之百的實力跑是山道常識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.26,0:03:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過這輪就全力甩開你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.49,0:03:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都到這地步了實在不想輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何都要咬住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,86好不容易肯聽話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.24,0:04:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從沒這麼強烈地想贏過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為對手同樣是86嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之一定要用這輛車來贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.78,0:04:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.03,0:04:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千鈞一髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一不留神真的會很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是輸了就算完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.22,0:05:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來 我是疲倦了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才開始就感覺抓不準路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道...是輪胎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.47,0:05:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偏偏這時...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.62,0:05:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後輪堅持不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.66,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是後輪抓地力下降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形勢不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有輪胎毫無辦法解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.42,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然拼到了這個地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能還是不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.89,0:05:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會就此輸掉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.02,0:05:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.34,0:05:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的節奏應該下降了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.71,0:05:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻為什麼沒被前面的車拉遠?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.89,0:06:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 只有這樣才想得通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方也發生了和我一樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.01,0:06:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方的車輪也打滑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.55,0:06:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是第四輪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.37,0:06:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出人意料地成了消耗戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.02,0:06:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方的後輪衰減也應該很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.47,0:06:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬力提升的話 這負擔也會直接作用在輪胎上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.70,0:07:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彼此都是提升了馬力的車 以同樣的節奏持續跑到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.07,0:07:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輪胎在差不多的時候不行了也不足為奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.09,0:07:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害 從後面看得很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.81,0:07:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,條件越惡劣 他的跑法反而越嫻熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但對方也是有血有肉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.53,0:07:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先忍受不住的人就會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在比的是耐力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輪胎抓地力下降容易打滑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.80,0:08:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而更容易瞭解這車在極限領域中的跑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫無彆扭感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能隨心所欲的操控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能駕馭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我的86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基本是靠油門來轉向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點和以前的車一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但和以前不同之處...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡情讓它滑行的話就能清楚瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.95,0:09:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白這車的跑法了 老爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...現在是第幾輪了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.02,0:10:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭腦中也一片空白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經相當疲倦了 但...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.09,0:10:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.86,0:10:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且到了這種時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.64,0:10:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相比之下 後追的人比先行的人更費神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.14,0:10:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使速度稍有差異也無法在這條賽道超車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.48,0:10:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要輸也只有在後面追時被甩開而輸掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.84,0:10:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說前面跑的時候是不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著是有塌方的彎道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.22,0:10:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼努力 旁邊也沒空隙能插進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算能喘口氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.76,0:10:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞧著吧 在你忍耐不住出現失誤前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要跑多少輪我都奉陪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.71,0:11:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.29,0:11:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,砂土磨得比剛才平了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.44,0:11:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別做蠢事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.91,0:11:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是不可能超車的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.46,0:11:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼人啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.31,0:11:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.59,0:12:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒注意到每次有車橫排而過就會削去塌方的砂土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.61,0:12:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且從那微小縫隙精準入彎的技術...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.11,0:12:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙...不是一般的厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.74,0:12:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速度慢了下來 看來有結果了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.50,0:12:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰贏了? TRUENO還是LEVIN?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是TRUENO 拓海贏了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.29,0:12:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海那小子真行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.91,0:12:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥他們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.56,0:13:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.31,0:13:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算平安歸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是筋疲力盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上來吧 和美 回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.65,0:13:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那再見了 樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連再見都說不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.84,0:14:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的還能再見嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.46,0:14:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.37,0:14:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比賽怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贏是贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.11,0:14:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎...你真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.21,0:14:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就完全不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.63,0:14:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海你費心為我著想 還幫我製造機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.91,0:14:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可想說的話 我一句都沒說出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.68,0:15:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天起就一直在想和美的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.60,0:15:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從喜歡上和美後開始明白...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.44,0:15:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜歡一個人竟然會這麼痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.19,0:15:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦喜歡上了就會認真起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.14,0:15:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以無力挽回之時心臟就會感到撕裂般的痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也許會笑我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能理解?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很晚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.37,0:16:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離送貨只剩一小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.97,0:16:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 我要好好睡會兒 到時叫醒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.06,0:16:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.67,0:16:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒想到車會那麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.68,0:16:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 老爸 有空的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.44,0:16:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次教教我有關引擎的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.54,0:16:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是吹的什麼風?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.40,0:16:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了自己嚴重欠缺的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.09,0:17:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 樹那小子有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.59,0:17:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正遲早會知道 我就說了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.27,0:17:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 事情成了這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還以為進展很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又變回孤獨車手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.59,0:17:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.15,0:17:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.71,0:18:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了? 不是回埼玉了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時太急了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來拿留在這兒的行李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.62,0:18:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但留下的不只是行李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.10,0:18:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前太過匆忙 沒好好和你道別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.97,0:18:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和美 現在有時間嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一小時就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒問題 可你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.06,0:18:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說個人原因要早退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.33,0:18:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.91,0:18:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,揮灑青春啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.14,0:18:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這事對他來說比什麼都重要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.40,0:18:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你女朋友夏樹好像開始打工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.45,0:18:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們倆進展如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.59,0:18:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茂木?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅葉季也要結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.02,0:19:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會忘記秋名的紅葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.47,0:19:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次葉子變紅時一定會想起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.03,0:19:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來群馬遇到的朋友們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.22,0:19:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人中最特別的他 雖然有些臭美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.29,0:19:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但卻比誰都溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.36,0:19:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經常鼓勵我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.54,0:19:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小我一歲 就像是弟弟般的男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永遠...絕對...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.98,0:19:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.42,0:20:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要在這兒用餐嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見 和美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.83,0:20:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然說不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我是喜歡你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.27,0:21:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥 群馬選拔隊的編制怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.30,0:21:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,候選人已有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.18,0:21:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著就看他同不同意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能總是輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.54,0:21:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Emperor也好 秋名86也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會來復仇的

